---
/**
 * ThemeToggle — prototype `.theme-toggle` control.
 *
 * Verbatim DOM from `landing-static.html` (lines 156-159): two buttons wired to
 * `[data-theme-set]`. `theme.js` reads the clicks, sets `html[data-theme]`,
 * persists `localStorage["weave-theme"]`, and syncs `aria-pressed`. The initial
 * `aria-pressed` reflects the prototype's default `data-theme="dark"`.
 */
---

<div class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle">
  <button data-theme-set="dark" aria-pressed="true">Dark</button>
  <button data-theme-set="light" aria-pressed="false">Light</button>
</div>
